MID_支援_アクア_サクラ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmサクラ|3$w0|$Wsサクラ|$WaBig Sister Aqua...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaOh Sakura, did you come\nto hear a scary story?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E苦,|N-no! But...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaWhat's wrong?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaOut of all the stories you told me Big\nSister Aqua, I remembered the one story.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaWhich story?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaUmmmm... the one about the\nphantom of the Nohr castle.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|…………$k$p$E笑,|Oh that one! I remember. It was a story\nI had heard from a maid at the time...$k$pThat there was a portrait of\nan old gentleman in the lobby.$k$pEach and every night...$k$pHe would come out of the painting, kidnap\nthe maids and then drag them into hell.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$Eやけくそ,汗|WAHhhh!! Wahhhhh! You don't have\nto tell me now～!! P-please stop～!!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|Hehehe... Oh yes, this\nis how the story went.$k$p$E怒,|On a night with no moon...$k$pOne of the maids apparently\nheard someone walking around.$k$pShe said that no one would go\nwalking around so late at night...$k$pAnd that the sound was really strange,\nand peculiar enough, so she remembered.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E苦,|…………$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Feeling uneasy, she stayed up\nall night without sleeping a wink.$k$pWhen she left her room, rubbing her\nsleepy eyes, the castle was in chaos.$k$pWhat was strange was...only half of\nthe maids that were on duty remained.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E怒,|...!$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaShe asked everyone,\nwhere's this girl, and this girl?$k$pWas it that they overslept, or were late?\nIf they had, they'd get scolded...$k$pHow do you think everyone replied?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaI-I don't know...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|...That they didn't know these girls.\nThey'd never seen or heard of them.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E苦,|A-ahhhhh...!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|The girl tried to find any evidence of\ntheir existence, but couldn't find a thing.$k$pAnd of course, their rooms were empty...\nSuddenly, she remembered...$k$pThe story about the man in the\nportrait that kidnapped people!$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$Eやけくそ,|Eee-eeeeeeek!!!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|Because she heard the strange footsteps,\nperhaps she was next to be kidnapped.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E苦,照|Wahhhhh! Even though I told you to stop!\nThis is scary. Too scary, Big Sister Aqua!!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|Hehehe... even though you said that,\nyou still listened quietly to the rest of it.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaBu-but... I was so curious!\nB-because of you, Big Sister Aqua...$k$pI won't be able to visit the privy at night!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,|Really? Then I'll go with you,\nso tell me when you do.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$Eやけくそ,|P-please don't treat me like a child～!$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaHehehehe.$k
MID_支援_アクア_サクラ_Ａ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmサクラ|3$w0|$Wsアクア|$WaWhat's wrong Sakura?\nYou seem deep in thought.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaW-well... I was thinking\nabout you, Big Sister Aqua...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaEh, Me?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaYes, the scary story from the other time...\nYou looked so happy when you told me.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaAh... well... it's true that I got\npretty excited seeing you scared...$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E苦,|When I was little I heard...\nthat Big Sister Aqua...$k$pYou were always unsociable and\ndidn't really get along with people...$k$pThere were a lot of\nrumors about you too...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Sakura...$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaWhen I heard such heartless words,\nthere were so many times where I...$k$pI wanted to tell them that they were\nwrong... that you were fun and talkative.$k$pThat you were a person\nthat could smile warmly...$k$pBut I didn't have the courage...\nSo I was always drowned in such words...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|Thank you... Sakura.\nFor bearing this burden alone.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaI wanted everyone to know about\nBig Sister Aqua's good side...$k$pBut I didn't have the courage to do that...\nI'm a terrible... little sister...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaOf course not, it was my fault after all.$k$pNot only were you hurt by these feelings,\nbut you were also worried by such a thing.$k$pAll of this happened because I couldn't\nstand up for myself. It's my responsibility.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E通常,|Big Sister Aqua...$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaSakura, from now on, I'll learn how\nto talk to many different people.$k$pI'll do my best to be honest\nand learn more about myself.$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaO-okay...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,|That's why I'll show courage with\nSakura and take it one step at a time.$k$pIf we're together, it\nwon't be so scary, right?$k\n$Wsサクラ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes, of course Big Sister Aqua!$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaHehehe, thank you Sakura. I am blessed\nto have a little sister like you...$k\n$Wsサクラ|$WaOf course I feel the same way! Please take\ncare of me from now on, Big Sister Aqua.$k
